train_X = train_data['Metascore'].values
train_Y = train_data['Rating'].values

print(train_X.shape)
train_X = train_X.reshape(len(train_X), 1)
print(train_X.shape)

# Build the Model
reg = LinearRegression()
reg.fit(train_X, train_Y)
pred_Y = reg.predict(train_X)

print('Accuracy -', reg.score(train_X, train_Y))
print('Accuracy -', r2_score(train_Y, pred_Y))
